# Testing — mandatory for agents

Read [`docs/testing-policy.md`](../docs/testing-policy.md) before changing logic, content, or scripts.

## Every non-trivial session

1. After code changes → `npm run verify` (must pass).
2. New/changed pure logic → co-located `*.test.ts` or extend existing suite.
3. Content/safety copy → must pass `src/test/safety-copy.test.ts`.
4. Before handoff → `npm run test:audit`; fix actionable warnings.
5. n4l → `notes_test_run_checkpoint` with verify result.

## Lean suite

- One test file per source module; no duplicate scenarios.
- Do not add E2E without approval.
- Never weaken `src/test/safety-rules.ts` without Security agent review.
- Delete obsolete tests with removed features.

## Do not

- Skip tests because "user didn't ask".
- Commit with red `npm run verify`.
- Add snapshot tests of full `content.bundle.json`.
